[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "チッ……今日はダメだ……\nロクなのが居やしねえ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01007",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01008",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あのわがまま王妃め……\n次々注文を付けてきやがって",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01009",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "その分報酬は弾んでもらわねえと、\nまったく割に合わねえってんだ……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01010",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "っ……誰だ！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01011",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "…………",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01012",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "出てきやがれ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01013",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "っ！　爆弾！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01014",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "っ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01015",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "今のは音だけのオモチャだ。何者だお前",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01016",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あの、私は諸島同盟の監察官です。\n「ヌルスラの鷹」という賞金首を探しています",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01017",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ほう、ぽやっとした嬢ちゃんが監察官。\nそれは見抜けなかったぜ。なんで俺をつけてた？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01018",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……あなたの歩き方です。\n最初は変な歩き方をしてるなって思っただけでした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01019",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "でも、思い出したんです。あれは、ぬかるみを\n歩くときの歩き方……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01020",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "きっとあなたは長年ぬかるんだ地面を歩き続けて、\nその歩き方が染みついてしまったんです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01021",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "たとえば……湿地の多い、ヌルスラの地面のような",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01022",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "たったそれだけで犯罪者扱いってか？\nそんなの言い掛かりなんじゃねえか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01023",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "最初はただの勘でしたけど……\n今はより疑いが強まりました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01024",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ただの護身用だよ。\nそんなもの、なんの証拠にも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01025",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "これ、昔ヌルスラの闇市で見かけたことがあります。\n爆弾を模したオモチャ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01026",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ただ、同盟への加入をきっかけに、\nその手の闇市は一掃されたはず。なぜあなたがこれを？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01027",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "こんなものどこにだってある。\nどうしても俺をヌルスラと結び付けてえようだが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01028",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……インクのにじみ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01029",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "あ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01030",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ヌルスラは貧しい島です。\nなんにだってお金をケチります",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01031",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "だから商品に使われるインクだって安物。\nちょっと雑に扱っただけですぐにじんじゃう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01032",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "こんな安物のインクを使ってるの、\nヌルスラで作られたもの以外にありませんよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01033",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "適当言ってんじゃねえ！\nんなの、一目で分かるわけがねえだろ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01034",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "分かりますよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01035",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "だって、私も昔ヌルスラで、\nそんな商品を作ってたんですから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01036",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "目つきの悪い男",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……面白え。\nあんた、いい勘してるぜ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_710_036_01037",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "それじゃ、やっぱりあなたは……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_01038",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]